{"tid":509473,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"日本動畫 100 週年紀念影片釋出","createTime":"2017-12-25T10:57:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T06:29:51.000Z","uid":87540,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e3419f7b2e18d122e24d1758894618eb47b21368","tid":509473,"uid":87540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T10:57:55.000Z","msg":"今年為紀念動畫 100 週年，日本展開了各式各樣的企劃。而官方在今日釋出了一段結合了 122 部從以前至今的動畫作品，以及紀念主題曲「翼を持つ者 ～Not an angel Just a dreamer～」而成的宣傳影像。<br />\n <br />\n　　該部影片是以日本最早的動畫作品《塙凹内名刀之巻》（1917 年）作為起頭，搭配集結合 23 組聲優、以及動畫歌手的紀念主題曲「翼を持つ者 ～Not an angel Just a dreamer～」，在長達 14 分鐘的影片中，帶過 122 部作品的影像，帶領觀眾穿越時光隧道，快速一覽日本動畫的演進史。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4t-GV4XcJak\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4t-GV4XcJak&d=ZOOWPitwjGLyUMxvqtd0s7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=6a6da100\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4t-GV4XcJak</a>"},{"pid":"b69736b91f55a49d7a07bd87b3d3a40ce95a8f24","tid":509473,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T11:02:35.000Z","msg":"首歌出左好耐都冇人講<br />\n不過我覺得首歌麻麻地"},{"pid":"d056b9166c7863ba0c5e651de84d610bb9c5defd","tid":509473,"uid":24282,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T11:09:17.000Z","msg":"睇到作畫質素既倒退<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd55fdbe92c06c65578b548e17d2227c694884c","tid":509473,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T11:24:25.000Z","msg":"無EVA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cbea78e6a098544bf695307e4ebbae9ad97bbc3","tid":509473,"uid":8307,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T11:26:12.000Z","msg":"啲畫面同首歌都幾唔夾下<br />\n極多名作都冇,有啲鳩屎野又唔知點解攝到落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127c1ed4df37f65a20b